  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d95\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dba\u0dd1\u0db8\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5 67\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "67 who tried to go to Australia by boat are trapped",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy says that yesterday (10th) 67 people who tried to go to Australia using an unprotected multi-day fishing vessel were arrested in the Eastern Seaboard.",
        "During a search operation carried out by the Sri Lanka Naval Ship Ranarisi, belonging to the Eastern Naval Command, the relevant vessel was inspected due to the observation of a multi-day fishing vessel that was unsafely loaded with more people.",
        "There, due to the confirmation that the relevant personnel had attempted to migrate to another country illegally, measures were taken to take custody of the Navy, and there 53 men, 06 women, 08 children and in addition 06 persons involved in the smuggling of the relevant personnel to another country were arrested. Steps had been taken.",
        "Information has been revealed that the relevant personnel have tried to go to Australia and the personnel taken into custody by the Navy are revealed to be persons in the age limits of 01 to 56 years residing in Mannar, Vavuniya, Mullaitivu, Trincomalee and Batticaloa.",
        "The Navy has taken steps to hand over the people taken into custody by the Navy to the Trincomalee Port Police for further investigation."
      ],
